I"z<p>Some Lovelace cards have support for header and footer widgets. These widgets fill up the whole available space in a card.</p>
<h2>Picture header &amp; footer</h2>
<p>Widget to show a picture as a header or a footer. A picture can have touch actions associated with it.</p>
